All true, but a somewhat unfair comparison.  Consider that the mage class/epic was underpowered, especially in the later expansions, which Verant acknowledged first by the xp fix (pets share xp), and second by *normalizing* the epic pet's dps -- I don't consider it an upgrade.<br>
<br>
Since mages rely on their pet as a fundamental part of their class (moreso than *any* other class), bringing the epic pet in line made us less crippled, not really more powerful.<br>
